//lih.kg/1416511</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"283f61d01fdb73ba5d00f5539ee1f6801c16edcf","tid":1416600,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:27:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"132d442cd72e0cd183ee3729a1040f87e22415f7","tid":1416600,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:27:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c724ebb19c8222139ff167cc044045da7180891f","tid":1416600,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:30:31.000Z","msg":"我覺得可以對外宣布暫停一段時間不合作運動<br />\n不過繼續突擊警局  我要警犬無得休息<br />\n然後和理非進場<br />\n跟返哂黑警啲野<br />\n勇武行太快 和理非跟唔到"},{"pid":"6f8951061be8fe3995949791e1ae733926722164","tid":1416600,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:31:21.000Z","msg":"推"}]}